snippet.title: Stupid Zombies Exterminator (by GameResort) - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Zombies have taken over the city, and it is your job to clean up this mess.

Fight your way through each room, shooting all zombies while avoiding any contact. Collect coins along the way to upgrade your guns and unlock new weapons.
